</li>
<li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="Hesiod" title="Hesiod">Hesiod</a>, <i>Theogony</i> 969–74; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Apostolos_Athanassakis" title="Apostolos Athanassakis">Apostolos N. Athanassakis</a>, <i>Hesiod. Theogony, Works and Days, Shield</i> (Johns Hopkins University Press, 1983, 2004), p. 56.</span>
