<li id="cite_note-60"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-60">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Nicholas F. Jones, <i>The Associations of Classical Athens: The Response to Democracy</i> (Oxford University Press, 1999), p. 125, citing <i><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inscriptiones_Graecae" title="Inscriptiones Graecae">IG</a></i> II<sup>2</sup>1363, dating <i>ca.</i> 330–270; Karl Kerényi, <i>Eleusis: Archetypal Image of Mother and Daughter</i> (Princeton University Press, 1967), pp. 110–111.</span>
