<li id="cite_note-84"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-84">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Strabo <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=lfMrAAAAYAAJ&amp;pg=PA25&amp;dq=ploutonion+OR+plutonion+OR+plutonium+inauthor:Strabo&amp;lr=&amp;as_drrb_is=q&amp;as_minm_is=0&amp;as_miny_is=&amp;as_maxm_is=0&amp;as_maxy_is=&amp;num=100&amp;as_brr=3&amp;cd=1#v=onepage&amp;q=ploutonion%20OR%20plutonion%20OR%20plutonium%20inauthor%3AStrabo&amp;f=false">14.1.44</a>; "Summaries of Periodicals," <i>American Journal of Archaeology</i> 7 (1891), p. 209; Hewitt, "The Propitiation of Zeus," p. 93.</span>
