<li id="cite_note-85"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-85">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Frederick E. Brenk, "Jerusalem-Hierapolis. The Revolt under Antiochos IV Epiphanes in the Light of Evidence for Hierapolis of Phrygia, Babylon, and Other Cities," in <i>Relighting the Souls: Studies in Plutarch, in Greek Literature, Religion, and Philosophy, and in the New Testament Background</i> (Franz Steiner, 1998), pp.  382–384, citing <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Photios_I_of_Constantinople" title="Photios I of Constantinople">Photius</a>, <i>Life of Isidoros</i> 131 on the dream.</span>
