<li id="cite_note-86"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-86">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Christiane Sourvinou-Inwood, "Reconstructing Change: Ideology and the Eleusinian Mysteries," in <i>Inventing Ancient Culture: Historicism, Periodization and the Ancient World</i> (Routledge, 1997), p. 137; <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georg_Luck" title="Georg Luck">Georg Luck</a>, <i>Arcana Mundi: Magic and the Occult in the Greek and Roman Worlds</i> (Johns Hopkins University Press, 1985, 2006, 2nd ed.), p. 505.</span>
