<li id="cite_note-90"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-90">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Clare Robertson <i>et al.</i>, <i>Drawings by the Carracci from British Collections</i> (Ashmolean Museum, 1996), p. 35.</span>
