<li id="cite_note-99"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-99">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Francis Adams, <i>The Seven Books of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paulus_Aegineta" class="mw-redirect" title="Paulus Aegineta">Paulus Aegineta</a></i> (London, 1847), p. 270; Dalby, <i>Food in the Ancient World</i>, p. 105; <i>Nouveau dictionnaire d'histoire naturelle</i>, p. 315.</span>
