<li id="cite_note-100"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-100">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_M._Riddle" title="John M. Riddle">John M. Riddle</a>, <i>Contraception and Abortion from the Ancient World to the Renaissance</i> (Harvard University Press, 1992), p. 42; <i>Nouveau dictionnaire d'histoire naturelle</i>, p. 315.</span>
