<li id="cite_note-102"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-102">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Lucifuga inumbratione pallescens</i> and <i>Tartareae noctis obscuritate furvescens</i>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Martianus_Capella" title="Martianus Capella">Martianus Capella</a>, <i>De nuptiis</i> 1.79–80; Danuta Shanzer, <i>A Philosophical and Literary Commentary on Martianus Capella's</i> De Nuptiis Philologiae et Mercurii<i> Book 1</i> (University of California Press, 1986), p. 171.</span>
