<li id="cite_note-105"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-105">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Homeric Hymn to Demeter</i>, lines 7–9, as cited by Radford, <i>Lost Girls</i>, p. 145; Clayton Zimmerman, <i>The Pastoral Narcissus: A Study of the First Idyll of Theocritus</i> (Rowman &amp; Littlefield, 1994), p. 2.</span>
