<li id="cite_note-107"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-107">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">"Death and Greek Myths," in <i>Greek and Egyptian Mythologies</i>, edited by Yves Bonnefoy (University of Chicago Press, 1991, 1992), p. 110.</span>
