<li id="cite_note-109"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-109">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">On the difficulty of identifying precisely which flower the ancients meant by "narcissus," see <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Claverhouse_Jebb" title="Richard Claverhouse Jebb">R.C. Jebb</a>, <i>Sophocles: The Plays and Fragments</i> (Cambridge University Press, 1900, 3rd edition), p. 115.</span>
