<li id="cite_note-162"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-162">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">J. van Amersfoort, "Traces of an Alexandrian Orphic Theogony in the Pseudo-Clementines," in <i>Studies in Gnosticism and Hellenistic Religions, Presented to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gilles_Quispel" title="Gilles Quispel">Gilles Quispel</a> on the Occasion of His 65th Birthday</i> (Brill, 1981), p. 13.</span>
