<li id="cite_note-193"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Pluto_(mythology)#cite_ref-193">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The questions of authorship involving the <i>De deorum imaginibus libellus</i>  and the <i>Liber Ymaginum deorum</i> ("Book of Images of the Gods") are vexed; Ronald E. Pepin, <i>The Vatican Mythographers</i> (Fordham University Press, 2008), pp. 7–9.</span>
